    <abstract>
        <para>This dataset is a catalogue of plant species observed in plant communities in Madeira and Porto Santo islands. It is based on the syntaxonomic and floristic catalogue of the plant communities of Madeira and Porto Santo, published on Quercetea vol. 6, published in 2004. The sampling is based on field trips performed in the same year. The Madeira and Porto Santo Vegetation Catalogue data includes 119 plant families.</para>
    </abstract>
